text: Love those Monte Carlo simulations of Markov unreliability models.

No tears from this bear on the name. I shorted it twice and made money both times. No dog in the hunt right now. I am objecting to the marketing (absent analysis) machine.

I call B.S. Cathie Wood now projects a price target of $TSLA of $3000 in 2025... How many times do you get to revise your already stupid price target up, on no new news about anything? ARK is a joke - just willy nilly make shit up, much like the sell-side.  Not analysts, just a

marketing machine. All the flak recently about short sellers, and people continue to get away with this garbage? Where is the financial media calling them out? NEW RULE – No price revisions. The more these stocks go down, the more these guys revise the target up.
